race.comment: The penny has dropped for HE'SGOTTHESAY (10) who has a win and two seconds from three starts this campaign with this mile trip being his pet distance. Looks the one they all have to run down. THE IRISH (2) is first-up here but has placed when fresh before and gets 3kg off with the claim. Should be there at the finish. SANCTUARY STORM (18) just ran into one better when resuming and will have come on with that run now under the belt. Sure to be hitting the line with gusto. TORO STRIKE (7) is usually thereabouts and shapes as one for the exotics players. HE'S A SAINT (9) next in line from the favourable draw.
